{
  "analysis": "The current terminal state shows we are logged in as the root user in the /home/user directory. No prior work has been done towards the task objectives. We need to create the directory structure, process the template, start the server, and generate the manifest.",
  "plan": "First, I'll create the required directory structure with the correct permissions. Then I'll process the template file according to the specifications (stripping BOM, performing substitution, and converting encoding). After that, I'll start the Python HTTP server in the background. Finally, I'll verify the deployment and generate the audit manifest file.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "mkdir -p /home/user/microservices/webroot\n",
      "duration": 0.1
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "chmod 2750 /home/user/microservices/webroot\n",
